## <a id="login"></a> Log in to <%= vars.product_short %>

Follow the steps below to log in to <%= vars.product_short %>.

1. Open a web browser and go to
<code>https<span>:</span>//service-instance-manager.YOUR-PIVOTAL-PLATFORM-FOUNDATION-URL</code>.

1. Log in with the email address and password you use for that <%= vars.platform_name %> foundation.

     <%= image_tag("images/cf-login-page.png", :alt => "Cloud Foundry login page", :width => "250") %>
  * If this is the only <%= vars.platform_name %> foundation that <%= vars.product_short %> is configured to target, the <%= vars.product_short %> UI appears.
  * If <%= vars.product_short %> is configured to target any other <%= vars.platform_name %> foundations, you are redirected to the
      login page for the next foundation listed in `config.json`. Redirects continue until you have logged in
      to every foundation that <%= vars.product_short %> targets.

1. Log in to each <%= vars.platform_name %> foundation until the the <%= vars.product_short %> UI appears.

